data.description: This cozy three-bedroom and two and half bath home is in a great location with quick access to schools, hospitals, shopping, and Closer to 215 and 10 freeways. The home is located within walking distance to the VA Hospital (From VA hospital right on Benton then again right on Cole St), Loma Linda University Hospital, Loma Linda Children's Hospital, and Drayson Center (The Loma Linda University Gym). All bedrooms are upstairs. The home features an open floor plan with a main-level dining area, a half bath and a two-car attached garage.
